    src/time.zig
    src/stdx/stdx.zig

All other files are BrainGang originals, including the package boundary
(src/lib.zig), the three minimal shims (src/constants.zig, src/trace.zig,
src/vsr/superblock.zig), the build scripts (build.zig, build.zig.zon),
the smoke tests (test/), and the manifest verification tool
(tools/check-manifest.sh).

The full upstream-vs-local file manifest, including the rationale for what
was pruned and what was synthesized, lives in UPSTREAM.md.
